videos.description: Rockets' WR Jon'Vea Johnson jumps way up to grab the touchdown pass from Logan Woodside to put Toledo on top.
videos.headline: Toledo climbs the ladder for stunning TD

videos.description: Logan Woodside tosses it out to Desmond Phillips who finds a hole on the sideline and takes off for a 40-yard score.
videos.headline: Screen turns to sideline-trot TD

videos.description: Danzel McKinley-Lewis darts across the middle of the field and catches the pass from Logan Woodside for a Toledo touchdown.
videos.headline: Woodside has 3 TD passes in 1st quarter

videos.description: Trickery offense from the Zips leaves Kobie Booker wide open for the 25-yard touchdown.
videos.headline: Flea flicker ends up in Akron TD

videos.description: Jon'Vea Johnson shows off with a stumbling, diving grab for the first down.
videos.headline: Toledo with acrobatic catch for first down

videos.description: Logan Woodside and Jon'Vea Johnson connect for a touchdown for the second time today on this 25-yard pitch and catch.
videos.headline: Woodside adds his 4th TD pass

videos.description: An incredible throw from Logan Woodside combined with a great effort to keep his feet in by Diontae Johnson leads to Woodside's 5th touchdown throw.
videos.headline: Woodside now has 5 TD passes

videos.description: Thomas Woodson airs it out from 17 yards and Tra'Von Chapman hauls in a nice catch in the back of the end zone.
videos.headline: Nice grab leads to Akron TD

videos.description: Robbie Kelley comes in and throws a 47-yard touchdown pass to Kwadarrius Smith for the Zips.
videos.headline: Akron backup QB tosses TD pass

videos.description: Shakif Seymour runs into a wall, but goes around and dives over the pylon to score.
videos.headline: Rockets score on rushing TD
